				<h1 id="about_header" class="text-center mb-3 mt-3">Welcome, Music Fan.</h1>

				<h4 class="text-secondary mb-0 mt-4 about_subheader">Lets start with this: we <strong class="text-danger">LOVE</strong> music.</h4>
				
				<p>In fact, just like you, we can go into seemingly endless detail about what we love on our favorite records. As streaming has become a larger part of the music industry, we started to find it harder and harder to keep track of all the great music in our libraries. We also noticed we were missing out on opportunities to share records we liked with our friends.</p>

				<h4 class="text-secondary mb-0 mt-4 about_subheader">Our solution?</h4>
				<p>To address this problem, we built an app where you can <a href="/search/">search</a> for music and write custom tags describing exactly what you love about it. You can then search these tags to find more music with similar qualities! And when words can't do your feelings justice, just manually connect one album to another so you can remember how they are related later.</p>
				<p>Not sure where to start? Check out our <a href="/favorites">favorite albums</a> of <%= thisYear %> so far. Want to try some other features? Poke around using the 'Site Navigation' menu above, or look at the videos below showing some of our favorite features of the app.</p>
			</div>
		
